name: Larissa Zeeuwe
profile:
Hello and welcome to my YouTube channel.
My name is Larissa, I'm a 21 year old Dutch film student and I love making YouTube videos.
I mostly make reaction videos, but beside that I also make game videos and vlogs.
I upload English and Dutch videos, (when I upload in Dutch with English subtitles).
I also have a Patreon and that allows you to get early acces, uncut videos, behind the scenes and more: Patreon.com/LarissaZeeuwe
I hope you like my channel and thanks for subscribing! :)
